# Design system & tokens

The full reference is **`DESIGN-SYSTEM.md`** at the repo root — read it first.

## Golden rules

- **Never hand-edit `src/styles/tokens.css`, `src/styles/tokens.ts`, or
  `figma-tokens.json`.** They are GENERATED. Editing token VALUES = edit
  `tokens/*.json`. Editing the CSS var contract (names/order/rgb companions) = edit
  `style-dictionary.config.mjs`.
- After changing either, run **`npm run tokens`** to regenerate (it also runs at the
  front of `npm run build` / `npm run dev`). Commit the regenerated files.
- **Keep `src/index.css` globals-only** — resets, base elements, `.btn*`,
  `.status-badge*`, `.status-dot*`, scrollbars, and the `prefers-reduced-motion`
  reset. Do NOT re-add token `:root` blocks there.

## Where things live

- `tokens/` — token VALUES (SOT), tiered: `color.palette.json` (primitives),
  `theme.dark.json` / `theme.light.json` (semantic + shadow, per mode),
  `radius.json`, `spacing.json`, `typography.json`, `motion.json`, `font.json`.
- `style-dictionary.config.mjs` — the emit plan + hex→rgb derivation + formats.
- `src/styles/tokens.css` — generated `:root` (dark) + `:root[data-theme="light"]`.
- `src/styles/tokens.ts` — generated typed maps + `ThemeMode`.
- `figma-tokens.json` (repo root) — generated one-way repo→Figma mirror manifest of
  the `cs.*` variable collections; synced to Figma by `figma-variables-sync.yml`.
- `src/styles/fonts.css` — self-hosted Inter (`@fontsource/inter`, weights 400/500/600).
- `src/lib/theme.ts` — sets `data-theme` on `<html>` (default dark).

## Conventions

- **rgb triplets are always derived from a hex** at build time — never hand-write a
  `*-rgb` value. Use `rgba(var(--x-rgb), α)` for soft tinted backgrounds.
- **Preserve dark/light parity**: any color added to one theme file should have a
  counterpart in the other unless it is genuinely mode-agnostic (then it belongs in
  a constant tier, emitted once in `:root`).
- **New scales (spacing/type/motion) are opt-in** — adopt on obvious, low-risk
  literals; do not attempt a repo-wide px→scale refactor in one pass.
- **Fonts**: code uses Inter (OFL); the Figma design uses Calibre — a deliberate
  licensed near-match. `--font-sans` = Inter then the system fallback stack.
- **Repo is the SOT; Figma mirrors it — and the mirror is LIVE.** Token values are
  projected into a Figma `cs.*` variable collection (pinned to Dark) via the generated
  `figma-tokens.json` (repo→Figma only; code never reads Figma). Figma **Code Connect
  is shipped**: source-tracked `src/**/*.figma.tsx` mappings (wired via the root
  `figma.config.json`) auto-publish to the Figma team library on every push to `main`
  (PRs get a `--dry-run`). See `design/divergence-ledger.md` for live mapping status
  (18+ mappings) and the divergence ledger.
